OL,3,CIconic bakery closes its doors after
OL,4,C120 years
OL,6,FA much-loved family-run bakery firm is
OL,7,Fclosing its doors for good after 120
OL,8,Fyears - after a prospective buyer
OL,9,Fpulled out of negotiations "at the
OL,10,Feleventh-hour".
OL,12,FLancashire bakery Oddie's employs more
OL,13,Fthan 100 people across its 13 stores
OL,14,Fin Burnley, Colne, Foulridge, Nelson,
OL,15,FPadiham and Todmorden, but it will be
OL,16,Fshutting up shop on 11 January for the
OL,17,Flast time.
OL,19,FA post on their website reads; "After
OL,20,F120 years we are closing our doors.
