OL,3,CIconic bakery closes its doors after
OL,4,C120 years
OL,6,F"The last day of trading will be
OL,7,FSaturday 11th January. We have loved
OL,8,Fbeing part of your lives."
OL,10,FIn November the company was put up for
OL,11,Fsale due to soaring costs and
OL,12,Fdeclining footfall.
OL,14,FBosses said an eleventh-hour
OL,15,Fwithdrawal by an unnamed buyer had
OL,16,F"left us with no choice but to
OL,17,Fconsider closure".
