OL,3,CIconic bakery closes its doors after
OL,4,C120 years
OL,6,FAfter four generations the family-run
OL,7,Ffirm had been hoping to secure an
OL,8,Furgent rescue deal to avoid closing
OL,9,Fall 13 locations and employed Azets,
OL,10,Fthe UK top ten accounting and advisory
OL,11,Ffirm, alongside Brabners Solicitors,
OL,12,Fin a bid to secure its future.
OL,14,FIn November, Lara Oddie, a director of
OL,15,Fthe bakery, said in a statement:
OL,16,F"Oddie's is a fourth-generation family
OL,17,Fbusiness, started in 1905 by William
OL,18,FHenry Oddie.
