OL,3,CIconic bakery closes its doors after
OL,4,C120 years
OL,6,F"Over the decades, it has withstood
OL,7,Ftwo world wars and their food
OL,8,Fscarcity, the Great Depression, the
OL,9,Ffall of Lancashire's cotton industry,
OL,10,Fthe rise of powerful supermarkets, and
OL,11,Feven the Covid-19 pandemic, which
OL,12,Fforced us to adapt our entire
OL,13,Foperating model.
OL,15,F"But with an energy crisis quadrupling
OL,16,Fcosts and footfall declining on the
OL,17,Fhigh streets, the Oddie family decided
OL,18,Fit was time to sell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
