OL,3,CIconic bakery closes its doors after
OL,4,C120 years
OL,6,F"Sadly, an eleventh-hour withdrawal by
OL,7,Fthe buyer has left us with no choice
OL,8,Fbut to consider closure.
OL,10,F"As a family firm, we have always seen
OL,11,Fourselves as part of the local
OL,12,Fcommunity fabric, making this a
OL,13,Fheartbreaking situation for us, our
OL,14,Fdevoted staff, and the loyal customers
OL,15,Fin Burnley and Pendle who have
OL,16,Fcherished our our unique products."
